                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-158-off798 t18280911-158-cd799"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280911-158-victim918" type="victimName">
                        John 
